                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9197" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1381</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1161 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当高杠杆遇上猪周期：正邦科技的大起大落</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">When the hog cycle meets high financial leverage: The ups and downs of Zhengbang Technology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵健梅，欧阳才越，王曼欣，蒋心悦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西正邦科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">正邦科技；高杠杆；猪周期；财务困境</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Zhengbang Technology, high leverage, hog cycle, financial distress</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例详细剖析了中国生猪养殖行业曾经的龙头企业——正邦科技的兴衰历程。正邦科技的创始人林印孙从一家饲料厂起步，于21世纪初带领公司转型进入生猪养殖领域并成功上市。非洲猪瘟爆发后，超级猪周期进入上行阶段，正邦科技加大杠杆激进扩张，成长为全国第二大猪企；然而，随着生猪价格的下行，公司开始面临巨额亏损和流动性危机，最终因资不抵债陷入退市危机，进行破产重整。通过对正邦科技在猪周期不同阶段的战略选择、经营举措和财务后果进行深入研究，分析高杠杆扩张模式如何影响正邦科技的兴衰，让学生思考，企业应当如何基于自身经营风险选择恰当的财务策略，合理控制杠杆水平，从而跨越周期，实现可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case details the rise and fall of Zhengbang Technology, a former leading enterprise in China&#39;s pig breeding industry. Lin Yinsun, the founder of Zhengbang Technology, started from a feed mill, led the company&#39;s transformation into the pig breeding industry in the early 21st century and successfully listed. After the outbreak of African swine fever, the super hog cycle began to rise, Zhengbang Technology increased leverage for radical expansion and grew into the second largest pig enterprise in the country. However, with the decline of pig prices, the company began to face huge losses and liquidity crisis, eventually fell into the risk of delisting due to insolvency and went through bankruptcy restructuring. Through the research on the strategic choices, business measures and financial consequences of Zhengbang Technology in different stages of the hog cycle, the case analyzes how the expansion mode with high leverage affects the development of Zhengbang Technology, and allows students to think about how enterprises should choose appropriate financial strategies based on their own business risks and control the leverage level, so as to go through the cycle and achieve sustainable development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">可持续增长率；经营风险；财务风险；总风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
